          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-5">
        <img
          width="384"
          height="193"
          class="h-auto mx-auto max-w-sm w-full"
          src="https://ik.imagekit.io/thegoldendino/rvcd/posts/magic-hour/IMG_6363_VZSSixVXK.jpeg?updatedAt=1687924448906&tr=w-384,h-193,f-jpg,pr-true"
          alt="Mural sponsored by Rainier Beach Action Coalition"
        />
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-sm mt-2 flex gap-3">
          <div class="font-bold text-xl">5.</div>
          <p class="text-sm">
            Rainier Beach Action Coalition
